[SN]TITLE[SN]
Teenager arrested over death of Patrick Ferguson in Croftfoot

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
An 18-year-old man has been arrested in connection with the death of a man who was found badly injured in a Glasgow street.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 48-year-old victim, who has been named as Patrick Ferguson, died shortly after police were called to reports of a disturbance in Midcroft Avenue, Croftfoot, at 02:25 on Friday.
The teenager being detained is expected to appear in court on Monday.
Police Scotland said a report would be sent to the procurator fiscal.
